      <h1>About Soundbolt</h1>

      <p>
        Soundbolt is a non-commercialized clone site of SoundCloud.
        It is designed by Raymond Gao and is intended to serve as the capstone project for the final stage of App Academy.
      </p>

      <p>
        The site borrows numerous concepts from the actual SoundCloud, but also has extended visual and interactive features that provide user with a different musical experience.
        With sound content from the Creative Commons community, the site is powered with productions from artists who believe in the open-source culture.
      </p>

